{"tid":602862,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"(大發現) 劉青雲曾演出王家衛電影","createTime":"2018-03-23T09:12:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-11T05:47:41.000Z","uid":134071,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ab2519162bea07aa6735f5c8123f0201b230aa47","tid":602862,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T09:12:03.000Z","msg":"後來套戲中途停拍, 「永高」告王家衛毀約............ 其中兩個演員後來係《重慶森林》重生<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/hkent168/photos/a.1043085945823325.1073741885.200180816780513/1234866023311982/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkent168%2Fphotos%2Fa.1043085945823325.1073741885.200180816780513%2F1234866023311982%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=hNXgKv16K%2FAoYbsNLvoNVTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=863bd88e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/hkent168/photos/a.1043085945823325.1073741885.200180816780513/1234866023311982/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n【1993年 《旺角火宅之人》開鏡】<br />\n1993年11月15日，王家衛與「永高」合作的《旺角火宅之人》開鏡，王導揚言電影會在兩個月內完成。演員陣容包括林青霞、梁家輝、王靖雯、劉青雲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/170856_11f5315d0fdebb3df4e4554339df02f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F170856_11f5315d0fdebb3df4e4554339df02f2.jpg&h=3bbb0ab9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e6e47d92a10a1fc123030aa89758d791729f1fd4","tid":602862,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T09:17:11.000Z","msg":"王家衛真係勁話唔拍就唔拍"},{"pid":"aefcf441424c9f23b2f877db60cbcd9087975f1f","tid":602862,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6e47d92a10a1fc123030aa89758d791729f1fd4","tid":602862,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T09:17:11.000Z","msg":"王家衛真係勁話唔拍就唔拍"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T09:18:50.000Z","msg":"佢鍾意邊拍戲邊寫劇本<br />\n<br />\n覺得無靈感, 就唔拍落去, 真係唔奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdf2719